{"tid":1093150,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【小組討論】如何防止比人劇透 avenger 4","createTime":"2019-04-05T11:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T04:36:03.000Z","uid":61443,"like":31,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0289f064375d2a028032c90c97da0194515c93","tid":1093150,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔想劇透？<br />\n因為唔知劇情睇先係最好睇 <br />\n個道理就係禮物未拆包裝前嘅心情  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世道已經覺得劇透人地係冇禮貌 <br />\n有啲有禮之人討論劇情之前<br />\n會先問下人地睇咗未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然中意比人劇透都冇問題 <br />\n不過呢個post應該唔適合你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中意劇透人地嘅話 <br />\n地獄最低層嘅煉獄等緊你  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分享避開技巧：<br />\n<br />\n* 唔睇預告 <br />\n預告根本係自殺劇透 <br />\n細佬十幾年冇睇 <br />\n近幾年都多人明咗呢個道理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n* 避開劇透撚<br />\n呢啲撚樣以劇透為樂<br />\n最好避之則吉<br />\n其實打到佢地入廠都唔過分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n* 避上連登 <br />\n係連登post 中個好多次槍 <br />\n我諗都已經有好多人明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n* 避上YouTube <br />\n近幾年有時上yourube睇下片<br />\n掃過都比幅圖同標題劇透咗 <br />\n個感覺似行街都比人捅咗刀咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n* 避上媒體網站<br />\na3 上之前都比 unwire 劇透到 <br />\n一個科技網都劇透到你電影 <br />\n你就知媒體網站好恐怖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*** 小心玩具 *** <br />\n近幾年好興<br />\n電影上之前出定玩具等人買 <br />\nhot toys 同 LEGO <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經中過好撚多獲槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32136c7708ad46d684380c9a7051ee77f018f7dd","tid":1093150,"uid":34123,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"真係辛苦"},{"pid":"57651008b815875612e7a98f44a3a63d62650164","tid":1093150,"uid":154796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"唔好睇蘋果<br />\n成日個標題已經劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2253097e17be05eed08293181d829a60f4b6b36c","tid":1093150,"uid":61443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57651008b815875612e7a98f44a3a63d62650164","tid":1093150,"uid":154796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"唔好睇蘋果<br />\n成日個標題已經劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"網媒都唔敢上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f638cc29d8f95396d55b016929048b4334b9e54e","tid":1093150,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85f0cbee4b5907dca2a64d5af9be2fb3e863b4a","tid":1093150,"uid":128660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43023f6641cb6a890b4bd409f49886011bcba87","tid":1093150,"uid":11254,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"扑暈自己幾日"},{"pid":"87b198681b925e3f95c69f629aa1c09dd5c5e469","tid":1093150,"uid":1778,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"上一場戲散水D人會唔覺意劇透，你自己小心啦<br />\n我就睇頭場，冇人透到我"},{"pid":"011b7436ff6732445512d0c86f1d666d647d0729","tid":1093150,"uid":81882,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"反而我鐘意比人劇透先<br />\n知道少少，會更有期待感想知全部<br />\n會估！<br />\n睇書我都會睇尾個章先"},{"pid":"d4e8ba6714f47189ac37c427adc8175dc9194e22","tid":1093150,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"